history.content: I am a Fall 2020 junior transfer and I plan on declaring as data science at the end of this semester. I have completed all the requirements to declare CS expect CS70. If I take CS70 over the summer and meet the requirements could I also declare CS by the end of this summer?
history.subject: Declaring CS as a transfer
